{"type":"message","id":"ce5b8913","parentId":"02977008","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:25:06.874Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_883616b443434c61a8540679","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773123906873}}
