{"type":"message","id":"64ab3092","parentId":"50033476","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:29:11.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据获取完成，现在需要按照预警规则过滤数据并生成预警消息推送给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在根据预警规则过滤数据：\n\n**预警规则回顾：**\n- 通用规则：下跌 > 3% 或 上涨 > 5%\n- 中国石油专属：涨幅 > 2% 或 跌幅 > 1%\n\n**满足条件的股票：**\n1. 中国石油 (601857): -7.51% < -1% ✓ (专属规则)\n2. 中海油服 (601808): -6.82% < -3% ✓ (通用规则)\n3. 广汇能源 (600256): -5.36% < -3% ✓ (通用规则)\n4. 海油工程 (600583): -4.13% < -3% ✓ (通用规则)\n5. 石化机械 (000852): -3.92% < -3% ✓ (通用规则)\n\n现在生成预警消息并推送：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4442de540b954e078a6fe4be","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n根据预警规则过滤股票数据并生成预警消息\n\"\"\"\nimport json\n\ninput_path = '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt'\noutput_path = '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-data.txt'\n\n# 读取数据\nstocks = []\nwith open(input_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    lines = f.readlines()\n    header = lines[0].strip()\n    for line in lines[1:]:\n        parts = line.strip().split(' | ')\n        if len(parts) >= 5:\n            stocks.append({\n                'code': parts[0],\n                'name': parts[1],\n                'price': parts[2],\n                'change_pct': parts[3],\n                'change_amt': parts[4],\n                'time': parts[5] if len(parts) > 5 else ''\n            })\n\n# 预警规则\ndef check_alert(stock):\n    \"\"\"检查是否满足预警条件\"\"\"\n    name = stock['name']\n    change_pct_str = stock['change_pct'].replace('%', '')\n    try:\n        change_pct = float(change_pct_str)\n    except:\n        return False\n    \n    # 中国石油专属规则\n    if name == '中国石油':\n        if change_pct > 2 or change_pct < -1:\n            return True\n    else:\n        # 通用规则\n        if change_pct < -3 or change_pct > 5:\n            return True\n    \n    return False\n\n# 过滤预警股票\nalerts = [s for s in stocks if check_alert(s)]\n\n# 按涨跌幅排序\nalerts.sort(key=lambda x: float(x['change_pct'].replace('%', '')))\n\n# 输出预警数据\nwith open(output_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(\"⚠️ 股价预警\\n\\n\")\n    f.write(\"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\\n\")\n    f.write(\"|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\\n\")\n    for s in alerts:\n        f.write(f\"| {s['code']} | {s['name']} | {s['price']} | {s['change_pct']} | {s['change_amt']} | {s['time']} |\\n\")\n    \n    f.write(\"\\n⚙️ 预警规则\\n\")\n    f.write(\"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\\n\")\n    f.write(\"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\\n\")\n    f.write(\"• 中国石油专属：🟢 涨幅 > 2% | 🔴 跌幅 > 1%\\n\")\n\nprint(f\"共 {len(alerts)} 只股票触发预警\")\nfor s in alerts:\n    print(f\"  {s['code']} {s['name']}: {s['change_pct']}\")\n\n# 输出推送消息内容\nmessage = \"⚠️ 股价预警通知\\n\\n\"\nmessage += \"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 |\\n\"\nmessage += \"|------|------|--------|--------|-------|\\n\"\nfor s in alerts:\n    message += f\"| {s['code']} | {s['name']} | {s['price']} | {s['change_pct']} | {s['change_amt']} |\\n\"\n\nmessage += \"\\n⚙️ 预警规则\\n\"\nmessage += \"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\\n\"\nmessage += \"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\\n\"\nmessage += \"• 中国石油专属：🟢 涨幅 > 2% | 🔴 跌幅 > 1%\\n\"\n\n# 保存消息内容\nwith open('/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-message.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(message)\n\nprint(f\"\\n预警消息已保存到 alert-message.txt\")\n","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/filter_alerts.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773124131977}}
